{"tid":1780775,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Microsoft 下個月起開始用全螢幕提醒你由 Windows 7 升級到 Windows 10 系統","createTime":"2019-12-12T15:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T15:10:39.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5dad9fe069c8a0f9ab331483b5d709a1af18def2","tid":1780775,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:44:19.000Z","msg":"明年 1 月 15 日起，微軟針對未購買延伸安全更新的 Windows 7 電腦，將顯示全螢幕的系統安全警告通知，提醒用戶升級到 Windows 10。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s4.itho.me/sites/default/files/styles/picture_size_large/public/field/image/1212-sheng_ji_win_10.png?itok=SWDmnXx1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs4.itho.me%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fpicture_size_large%2Fpublic%2Ffield%2Fimage%2F1212-sheng_ji_win_10.png%3Fitok%3DSWDmnXx1&h=884d1dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據微軟支援網頁從 2020 年 1 月 15 日起，Windows 7 電腦將顯示全螢幕的通知，告知用戶在大限之後仍繼續跑 Windows 7 SP1 的風險。這個通知會停留在畫面上，直到用戶與之互動為止。<br />\n<br />\n會出現這個通知的 Windows 7 版本包括簡易（Starter）、家用入門（Home Basic）、家用進階（Home Premium）、專業版及旗艦版。專業版用戶如果有買延伸安全更新（Extended Security Update，ESU）服務，電腦就不會出現這個通知。<br />\n<br />\n此外以同一網域串連的電腦，或是設定 Kiosk 模式的機器，也不會出現本通知。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/134781\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com.tw%2Fnews%2F134781&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fczr7MFgrQ0V0XG6LyL0fmAc%3D&h=ad6c0d7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/134781</a>"},{"pid":"1dede85097edf17478e275ee47b06a9d9f5a3106","tid":1780775,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"借po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發動世界級遊行！Who stand with us世界巡遊！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1780766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1780766</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d28fd5d44ae581be3bccd5dfa1884a23b9f51e07","tid":1780775,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply